latestPosts.caption:
Would you believe if I say pursuing MBA was a fluke?

My sister and I used to reside in delhi together and I was having a good time. In June 2023, she left as she graduated from DU. I felt homesick. As a Content Creator I felt purposeless. I asked myself Would I just want to be another content creator or utilise my golden period and upskill myself.

One Random day, my dad said “Beta why don’t you do MBA”? That thought stayed with me and that’s when I decided why not go back to my alma mater and relive my college days at UPES. Hence MBA Happened.

In this journey I met a few amazing people that I am gonna cherish for the rest of my life.

I am glad that from today onwards I have added a new feather in my hat, Presenting to you, Gautam Manchandani, Law Graduate, Content Creator and an MBA HR❤️

Just grateful for all good things happened in these 2 years. 

With That,
Signing off as a student and Loging in to the world of Corporate and maximise my potential to unlock new horizons of HR.
